1
00:00:01,233 --> 00:00:04,133
-*- 用热情教学 -*-

2
00:00:05,233 --> 00:00:08,433
I think that passion is one of the few things
我认为热情是为数不多的

3
00:00:08,433 --> 00:00:11,266
that would take you into a vocation like teaching
让你进入教师这类职业的特质之一，

4
00:00:11,266 --> 00:00:13,266
which is generally so thankless
教师通常都是吃力不讨好，

5
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:16,800
and so demanding and so underpaid
要求很高、报酬很低，

6
00:00:16,900 --> 00:00:19,700
and so poorly valued in the society.
而且其价值被社会严重低估。

7
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:24,500
Passion is what most good teachers have in their guts
热情是大多数优秀老师的本能，

8
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:27,300
it's what makes them want to go into a classroom 
这就是为什么他们愿意走进教室

9
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:28,700
and serve the young.
并为年轻人服务。

10
00:00:28,966 --> 00:00:33,133
And it's not passion about going to a school of education
这不是因为去学校这件事有热情，

12
00:00:33,266 --> 00:00:35,666
which is often a very passionless place.
因为那里通常是个非常没有热情的地方。

13
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:38,400
It's passion about children,
这事关对儿童的热爱，

14
00:00:38,766 --> 00:00:40,400
it's passion about young lives
事关对年轻生命的热爱，

15
00:00:40,733 --> 00:00:42,000
it's passion about helping those young lives
事关对帮助年轻生命

16
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:45,933
to flower and grow
绽放和成长的热爱，

17
00:00:45,933 --> 00:00:49,666
and it's often passion about a subject 
而且往往事关对某个学科的热爱,

19
00:00:50,333 --> 00:00:51,933
maybe good literature 
也许是优秀文学作品,

20
00:00:52,766 --> 00:00:55,966
or physical or natural science or history.
也许是物理学或自然科学或历史学。

21
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:59,600
A lens through which you can see the world
通过学科这个镜头，你可以看到这个世界，

22
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:03,600
and a lens which for this teacher has
对这位教师来说，通过学科这个镜头，

23
00:01:04,433 --> 00:01:06,633
given him or her a broader view of the world，
让他或她对世界的了解有了更广阔的视角，

24
00:01:06,633 --> 00:01:09,533
a richer view of the world in a larger sense of self.
在更大的自我意识中，对世界有了更丰富的看法。

25
00:01:09,866 --> 00:01:12,900
And the teacher is passionate about wanting to help
老师热情帮助年轻人

26
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:16,100
some young people see the world through that lens
通过这些镜头了解这个世界，

27
00:01:16,166 --> 00:01:19,333
and enlarge their own sense of selfhood.
并扩展他们的自我意识。

29
00:01:19,333 --> 00:01:22,133
So passion is right at the heart of good teaching.
总而言之，热情是优秀教学的核心。
